# # Local Business Cafe

# ## Overview
# The Local Business Cafe is a fictional local business that requires a fully functional and responsive website to promote their cafe menu, including coffee, drinks, and snacks. This project implements the necessary features for the cafe's website.

# ## Pages
# - **Home Page**: Introduces the business and highlights its unique selling points.
# - **About Page**: Provides detailed information about the business.
# - **Contact Page**: Includes contact information and a contact form.
# - **Category Page**: Displays various menu categories.
# - **Products Page**: Displays products with descriptions, prices, and images.
# - **Cart Page**: Allows users to add and remove items from the cart and view the total price.

# ## Technologies Used
# - HTML
# - CSS
# - JavaScript

# ## How to Run
# 1. Clone the repository.
# 2. Navigate to the project directory.
# 3. Open `index.html` in your browser to view the homepage.

# ## Deployment
# The project is deployed on GitHub Pages. You can view the live site [here](https://your-username.github.io/local-business-cafe).

